rules:
  - folders:
      - src/
    instructions: >
      Use React Native with Expo for web + mobile.
      Prefer React Native Paper components.
      Use Firebase Firestore + Auth.
      This is an Expo React Native app that targets web and mobile.
      Use React Native Paper for UI and Firebase for data.
      All APIs (AI, OCR, etc.) go through Firebase Cloud Functions.
  - folders:
      - functions/
    instructions: >
      Cloud Functions written in TypeScript.
      Handle AI summaries, OCR, and Stripe logic.
      Use OpenAI and Google APIs securely.
